ivardefs.name: image_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates a relative path to an image that exists within the IG.

ivardefs.name: other_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the relative path of an additional non-page, non-image file that is part of the IG - e.g. zip, jar and similar files that could be the target of a hyperlink in a derived IG.

ivardefs.name: page_
ivardefs.desc: Information about a page within the IG.

ivardefs.name: rendering
ivardefs.desc: A pointer to official web page, PDF or other rendering of the implementation guide.

ivardefs.name: resource_
ivardefs.desc: A resource that is part of the implementation guide. Conformance resources (value set, structure definition, capability statements etc.) are obvious candidates for inclusion, but any kind of resource can be included as an example resource.

properties.desc: Information about an assembled implementation guide, created by the publication tooling.
